OL,3,CMountains of rubbish after tidal wave
OL,4,Cof plastic covers Bali beach
OL,6,FWatch diggers and locals try and clear
OL,7,Fup mountains of rubbish on Kedonganan
OL,8,Fbeach in Bali
OL,10,FA tidal wave of rubbish has left a
OL,11,Fnormally beautiful beach on Bali
OL,12,Fcovered in plastic, leaving tourists
OL,13,Fand locals desperately trying to clean
OL,14,Fit up.
OL,16,FIt happened at the Kedonganan beach in
OL,17,Fthe Kuta area of the island following
OL,18,Fa bleak annual event caused by a
OL,19,Fmonsoon.
