OL,3,CMountains of rubbish after tidal wave
OL,4,Cof plastic covers Bali beach
OL,6,FPictures show the sandy beach strewn
OL,7,Fwith discarded plastic bottles, cups
OL,8,Fand packaging, most of which is
OL,9,Fthought to have landed on Bali from
OL,10,FIndonesia's cities due to monsoon
OL,11,Fwinds and rains.
OL,13,FAround 300 officers and six diggers
OL,14,Fhelped to try and clear the rubbish,
OL,15,Falongside a local charity.
OL,17,FSome locals are said to have picked
OL,18,Fthrough the plastic for recyclable
OL,19,Fmaterial, which can be sold for a few
OL,20,Fdollars.
