OL,3,CMountains of rubbish after tidal wave
OL,4,Cof plastic covers Bali beach
OL,6,FBali depends on tourists, and the
OL,7,Fplastic covered beach were not what
OL,8,Fmany visitors had hoped for.
OL,10,FDenis Le Merre, from said: "I came
OL,11,Fhere because I heard that it was a
OL,12,Fvery nice place to visit, but what I
OL,13,Fsee is all of this plastic. It's a
OL,14,Freal disaster for me."
OL,16,F"It's impossible to bathe, swim and
OL,17,Fstay here. I think I will never come
OL,18,Fback."
OL,20,FEach year mountains of plastic waste
OL,21,Fwashes up on Bali's beaches.
