OL,3,CMountains of rubbish after tidal wave
OL,4,Cof plastic covers Bali beach
OL,6,FBut he is are now calling on people to
OL,7,Fstop littering.
OL,9,FAnak Agung Dalem said: "I call on all
OL,10,Fpeople in Indonesia, don't litter in
OL,11,Fempty lands, don't throw rubbish on
OL,12,Fcliffs and rivers because it will end
OL,13,Fup on sea and will arrive at our
OL,14,Fbeautiful beaches."
OL,16,FThe wave of rubbish on Kedonganan
OL,17,Fbeach is something that happens
OL,18,Fannually in the area according to
OL,19,FDalem due to the monsoon weather.
